metadata.name: Queer Formations | Series One
metadata.description:
Queer Formations | Series One is the Ai Collaborative Genesis Collection built between Fantastic Planet, Midjourney, and Stable Diffusion.  

The different forms I have taken during my life as a Queer Latinx Artist have been generated in this collaborative experiment. My feelings. Life Experiences. Men in my life. Friends I have lost. All of it starts with this Genesis Collection.

We are forever changing and forming as queer people. Forever re-forming again and again. To be seen as simply one thing, or one form isnâ€™t the reality. I have constantly shifted my shape, physically, emotionally, and spiritually. 

_______


As Genesis Collectors of these tokens, I grandfather Series One holders with forever pricing in future Queer Formations Series and editions. As this collection and experiment grow, those who have been here from this moment will always pay the mint price of this token for future pieces within the Queer Formations Collection.
